    <h2 class = "environmentalism">More Information </h2>
        </div>
    <p class = "environmentalism">In our modern society, sexism is more prevalent than people would like to think. Although primarily towards women, prejudice and discrimination on the basis of sex is a danger for everyone. From example to example, sexism may be exhibited in small, seemingly innocuous events. This may portray itself as a comment thrown out in the hallways of a high school, or a girl who walks into an office on her first day of work and realizes she is the only female present. However, these situations can snowball into long-term damage. Many activists are at work to change the mindset of sexism.
</p.>
