    <h2 class = "environmentalism">Important People </h2>
        </div>
    <p class = "environmentalism">Maya Angelou–she was an influential African-American poet and writer who staunchly refused to allow anyone to reduce her. “I can be changed by what happens to me. But I refuse to be reduced by it.”
<br>
Susan B. Anthony–she fought for women suffrage and founded the National Woman Suffrage Association.
<br>
Malala Yousafzai–this girl, a young activist, was shot in the head by the Talaban when she was fifteen because of all her efforts. She recovered and went on to write an autobiography and speak to various audiences, including Queen Elizabeth II and Barack Obama.
</p.>
